Requires:
libgnomeui-2.0
gtk+2.0
gdk-2.0


To compile:

 LDFLAGS="`pkg-config libgnomeui-2.0 --libs` `pkg-config gtk+-2.0 --libs` `pkg-config gdk-2.0 --libs`" CPPFLAGS="`pkg-config libgnomeui-2.0 --cflags` `pkg-config gtk+-2.0 --cflags` `pkg-config gdk-2.0 --cflags`" CFLAGS="-O0 -g3 " ./configure
 make

tested on Linux/Cygwin